      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i know i should reach out but it just feels like so much work. honestly it's not even about the crisis anymore, it's just this constant, heavy weight. i feel like everyone around me has so much purpose and i'm just... a void. an expensive, failed mistake. it’s like i'm just waiting for something to end so i can finally stop pretending i'm okay.",
